{"tid":667544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"下體滴蠟誆開脈輪　性侵5女還上訴要免刑","createTime":"2018-05-17T00:11:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T06:22:53.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9887398c0626adac38e6b0dca3a097358e2dd60e","tid":667544,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T00:11:36.000Z","msg":"1名廚師自稱「心靈講師」對外招生，專挑正妹加入群組，稱滴蠟油等可淨化及開脈輪，性侵5名女子去年被輕判6年，他再上訴要求免刑被駁回。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》曾報導，吳姓男子（36歲，在押）2016年起以心靈成長課程名義對外招生，再挑正妹到摩鐵私下免費「輔導」，現場擺放水晶陣、敲缽，再燃精油蠟燭，把蠟油抹在女子下體稱「開脈輪」，手指沾精油侵入下體、肛門，還要女子幫他口交等行為。<br />\n<br />\n新北地院認定吳男罹患精神疾病，僅依強制性交、猥褻等罪輕判吳男合併執行6年。今日出版的《聯合報》報導，吳男以自身的精神疾病為理由上訴，稱法官應用刑法第19條規定判他免刑，但合議庭不採納，高等法院駁回。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180517/640_b3e5ed094134d58684ce19757a412d6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180517%2F640_b3e5ed094134d58684ce19757a412d6e.jpg&h=f2e6c046&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳男打著「心靈講師」名號涉嫌性侵女學員。翻攝照片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180517/1355383/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180517%2F1355383%2F&d=QZGlUmFjcFsXdRC5pcKbX57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=f1a8d8c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180517%2F1355383%2F&h=3af39187\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180517/1355383/</a>"},{"pid":"ee1d9d38c0df9810043a36ba4e42f328e67e2263","tid":667544,"uid":157138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T00:15:24.000Z","msg":"樓主做咩狙擊台灣呢類新聞 連開三個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f0ec13e6d5aa66f54fd040a55213791e318872","tid":667544,"uid":86893,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T00:16:42.000Z","m